{"tid":594132,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有無逐漸變成自己細個個陣好憎嘅個種大人？","createTime":"2018-03-15T14:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T17:37:01.000Z","uid":39785,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a88b2a11584c7cae11784ef66fddbda94249b58b","tid":594132,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T14:46:19.000Z","msg":"細個個陣d 長輩最中意講<br />\n我食鹽多過你食米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家d 候生一代不如一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個聽到好撚憎<br />\n覺得佢地年齡歧視 倚老賣老<br />\n因為我遲過佢地出世 所以一世都畀佢地用呢d 說話踩住<br />\n<br />\n到依家大左d上連登<br />\n發現連登仔都係笑00後為樂<br />\n知道人地係00後就笑左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔定過多廿年 <br />\n依家班連登仔就會變成班跑住去爭凳仔<br />\n再鬧班候生唔讓座嘅死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ab5fa17d33e0ed4ca49e87ed972dbd36c45964","tid":594132,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c516261542e63339613c50ec177103feeb436da","tid":594132,"uid":39785,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"不服來辯！！"},{"pid":"c46729be393720e2e33ba97665914b94f990935b","tid":594132,"uid":56725,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9869d4ccf7daaf01e3763a65e525af7283ee553","tid":594132,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"屌 認真post 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434a6da3faa7396c753ec9063f5cac62ac119904","tid":594132,"uid":39785,"like"